Ubwoko bw’indwara z’indwara (COVID-19) ni in Ibihugu by’Uburayi na i Ubwami bw’Ubwami bw’Ubwami bw’Ibyinjirije, ku A Igice cyatandukanye ku i Igihugu, i mpuzamaguzi ya COVID-19 ni iri hagati mu Byose Ibihugu.
Ku bihereranye n’ibyabaye muri Italiyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n’ibintu by’inshingano byagombye gutuma bitegurira abarwayi bari bafite COVID-19, bizasaba ubucuti bw’amahanga, kandi bikaba bikunze kwitaho inshingano.
Ku itariki ya 31 Kigarama 2019, hari ibibazo by’impunemoniya byari bizwi n’ibibazo bitazwi, byaravuzwe muri Wuhan, mu kirere cya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, i Cyana Center for Control and Prevention yavuze ko umuyobozi w’indwara ari a kinyamakuru cyo coronavirus NONEAHA yavuze ko ari ikintu gikomeye cy’impumurizo cy’icyuma cya coronavirus 2 (SARS-COV-2).
Uhereye, i indwara yavuye ku ubwoko bwa SARS-COV-2 yitwa indwara y’indwara (COVID-19).
Ibihamya bigaragaza ko abantu bafite COVID-19 bafite indwara igiranye ubugwaneza, icyo gihe bafite indwara y’agapapuro k’impumura cyangwa batagira impumu, kandi abenshi muri ibyo bintu bishobora kugaruka.
Mu mimerere ya 14%, COVID-19 itera indwara ikomeye kuruta ibindi bisaba ko gufata ibitaro, mu gihe abantu 6 ku ijana basigaye bafite indwara zigoye zisaba kwita ku mutima.
Abarwayi bafite ibitaro bivuye ku COVID-19 ni ca 4%.
Muri iyi nyigisho, dusuzuma ibyifashijwemo mu bintu bihuje n’icyo kibazo cya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy’Uburayi/Umurimo w’Iby’ubutunzi (EU/EEA) n’Ubwami bw’Uburengero bwo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, maze tubigereranya n’Ubwami bwa Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
